quests.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is how to play! First, it would be a great idea if you could attempt to go to the north. Then, take a trip east. That done, travel north. And then, try to head west. Then, make an effort to move west. Then, go south. And then, pick up the fly larva from the table within the shower. And then, make an attempt to take a trip east. That done, try to move north. Then, you can place the fly larva into the chest. Once that's all handled, you can stop!

objective: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Your first objective is to travel north. After that, make an attempt to move east. Okay, and then, attempt to go to the north. After that, try to head west. With that over with, take a trip west. After that, try to travel south. If you can get through with that, recover the fly larva from the table. After that, make an effort to head east. After that, make an attempt to take a trip north. Once you get around to doing that, you can insert the fly larva inside the chest inside the cubicle. Got that? Good!
